description: BBQ Bus DC is bringing great BBQ to the streets for hungry Washingtonians at honest prices.Partners in life, partners in business and partners in crime, Che and Tadd Ruddell-Tabisola came up with the BBQ Bus together, and the rest was history. Catch them in Washington DC for barbecue pork, beef, and chicken sandwiches so good it will "broke da mouth," as our family in Hawaii likes to say. We're also glad to hook you up with orders of a la carte meats and family packs to go and a la carte meats.
name: BBQ Bus DC
